{"tid":106553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶少女玩機動遊戲斷安全帶　墮地重創","createTime":"2017-02-03T17:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T02:43:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06997e7a88536a70a51132ce36e9d3e0a6360948","tid":106553,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/photo/bkncn-20170203180548235-0203_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170203184007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170203180548235-0203_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170203184007&h=2018dddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遊樂場機動遊戲設施再發生恐怖意外！網傳重慶市一名十多歲少女，今日下午3時左右在豐都朝華公園內玩機動遊戲時，疑因安全帶斷掉，從半空飛墮地，身受重傷。事故發生後，警方及救護人員趕抵現場，將她送院搶救。另網傳傷者在送院搶救後無效死亡，惟有關說法未獲官方證實。 <br />\n<br />\n從網傳事發時的短片所見，肇事機動遊戲設施如一個「滾筒」般在空中360度旋轉，其間一名少女被吊在半空打轉，隨即被強大的衝力甩飛落地。現場有一兩名男子隨即上前為墜地少女進行搶救，而四周則聚集了不少遊客圍觀。"},{"pid":"d98b943129f74eacdcfe67a9e3d7764c8d328431","tid":106553,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637b1680fa68880a59f5ee2dc8eb438c78d4503b","tid":106553,"uid":19919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"80cbd6241e95dc4643f9472e8448edd3c77a43e4","tid":106553,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T19:36:42.000Z","msg":"咁都死唔去就真係奇蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前印尼玩過類似 fing得好勁 玩完一次發誓唔玩第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793504ef9652f3b9e739879d9a9ac835d2b29313","tid":106553,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T20:14:48.000Z","msg":"13億人 就咁就無左一個喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669239789f4270881623562cbfe55bc0d97aa284","tid":106553,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:43:46.000Z","msg":"大陸質素是是但但，死幾多人都唔會改"}]}